# Architecture

## NiFi

### Processors

- Ingest Processors
- Extract Objects
- GUIDE Registration
- Post to Error Table
- Routing Service
- Update Metadata Store
- GUIDE Update
- Post to IMS Data Lake
- MINT Processor
- Post to IDL
- Post to RMM Ingest Queue
- IDL Listener
- IMS Data Lake Listener
